  <h1>Electronic<br><span class="gradient-text">Plastic Toys</span></h1>
  <p>Sound, light, and interactive electronic functions integrated with in-house plastic manufacturing — stable performance and full compliance with US and EU regulations.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="marquee-strip"><div class="marquee-track"><span>Sound &amp; Light</span><span class="dot">·</span><span>Interactive Electronics</span><span class="dot">·</span><span>OEM</span><span class="dot">·</span><span>ODM</span><span class="dot">·</span><span>CE Compliant</span><span class="dot">·</span><span>ASTM F963</span><span class="dot">·</span><span>EN 71</span><span class="dot">·</span><span>Sound &amp; Light</span><span class="dot">·</span><span>Interactive Electronics</span><span class="dot">·</span><span>OEM</span><span class="dot">·</span></div></div>
<section><div class="container"><div class="cap-detail-grid">
  <div class="cap-detail-left">
    <div class="section-label reveal-up">Overview</div>
    <h2 class="reveal-up delay-1">Plastic and electronics co-engineered under one roof for reliable, compliant products.</h2>
    <p class="reveal-up delay-2">Electronic plastic toys integrate sound, light, and interactive electronic functions into durable plastic housings. With proven electronic solutions and in-house plastic manufacturing capabilities working in tandem, we ensure stable performance, reliable production consistency, and full compliance with US and EU regulations.</p>
    <p class="reveal-up delay-2">The advantage of our integrated approach is that plastic housing and electronic components are co-engineered from the start — eliminating interface problems and ensuring both aspects meet safety standards simultaneously.</p>
    <div class="cap-features reveal-up delay-3">
      <div class="cap-feature"><div class="cap-feature-icon">&#128266;</div><div><h4>Sound &amp; Audio Features</h4><p>Integrated IC-based sound modules with high-quality speaker output — tuned to specification and tested for consistent performance across production runs.</p></div></div>
      <div class="cap-feature"><div class="cap-feature-icon">&#128161;</div><div><h4>Light &amp; Visual Effects</h4><p>LED and lamp-based light features integrated into plastic housings — managed for power consumption, heat, and safety compliance.</p></div></div>
      <div class="cap-feature"><div class="cap-feature-icon">&#128293;</div><div><h4>Interactive &amp; Sensor Features</h4><p>Sensor-triggered and button-activated interactive features — designed for intuitive child use and robust durability under repeat operation.</p></div></div>
      <div class="cap-feature"><div class="cap-feature-icon">&#10003;</div><div><h4>Dual Compliance: Plastic + Electronics</h4><p>In-house plastic and electronics capabilities are co-managed — both aspects meet safety standards simultaneously, simplifying certification.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="reveal-up delay-2">
    <div class="cap-spec-box"><h3>Specifications &amp; Capabilities</h3>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">Manufacturing</span><span class="spec-val">Plastic Molding + Electronics Assembly</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">Electronic Features</span><span class="spec-val">Sound, Light, Interactive, Sensor</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">Audio</span><span class="spec-val">IC Sound Module + Speaker</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">Lighting</span><span class="spec-val">LED / Lamp Integration</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">Customisation</span><span class="spec-val">OEM &amp; ODM</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">Safety Standards</span><span class="spec-val">ASTM F963 / EN 71 / CE</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-key">Markets Served</span><span class="spec-val">US, EU, Global</span></div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:24px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:28px;"><h3 style="font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green-light);margin-bottom:16px;">Product Examples</h3><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.65;">Electronic learning toys · Sound and light figures · Interactive plastic toys · Musical toys · Light-up vehicles · Electronic action figures · Sensor-activated toys</p></div>
  </div>
</div></div></section>
